sentences: Roli Alexandra Xanxan Orial (born 30 December 1989), also known by her stage name Sabrina Orial or simply Sabrina and Sabrinatics, is a Filipina recording artist and acoustic singer of cover versions.
Acoustic Love Notes – featuring Joe D'Mango (2012)
Dota O Ako (Aikee featuring Sabrina, 2012; original singer featured Vanessa in 2011; Acoustic Version released also in 2012)
